        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "This bride is full adorned with the pearls and precious stones,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And plaits of gold her nature, the triune God, her own."
