        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Overcoming believers overcoming each day!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Blessed are those who are called to the marriage on the way!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "A wedding feast is waiting in the kingdom of the Son"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "For the bride has made herself ready, blessed are those who come!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "chorus"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "This precious bride is clothed with fine linen, bright and clean,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The righteousnesses stitched by the Lamb within our being;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "A Christ lived out each day is an overcoming life,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "‘Tis right and pure and holy; to her to live is Christ."
            }
          ]
